Package: claudeAgentR
Title: Claude Agent SDK for R
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R: person("First", "Last", email = "author@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: An R SDK for programmatically interacting with Claude Code CLI.
    Supports one-shot queries, multi-turn blocking conversations resumed by
    Claude session id, async streaming, hooks for tool interception, and MCP
    server integration.
